name: Impossible Cloud Network Token
description: ICN Protocol is a next-generation decentralized internet infrastructure layer. With decentralized hardware resources, a composable service application layer, and a secure HyperNode network, ICN intends to drive the future of the internet through an integrated ecosystem of permissionless participants, all running without a single point of trust. Anyone can provide resources to the hardware layer, develop services on the application layer, or secure the ecosystem through the HyperNode network and earn rewards.
